headline: WTW to Announce Fourth Quarter and Full Year Earnings on February 3, 2026
summary: LONDON, Jan. 13, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- WTW (NASDAQ: WTW), a leading global advisory, broking and solutions company, will announce its financial results for the fourth quarter and full year 2025 on Tuesday, February 3, 2026, before the market opens. The company will host a conference call to discuss its financial results at 9:00 a.m. Eastern Time on Tuesday, February 3, 2026.
